question_en: Which emperor founded the city of Jaipur?
question_hi: जयपुर के स्थल को किस महत्त्वनाथ ने शुरू किया।
explanation_en: Cao Bika founded the city of Jaipur. The city was later developed and made the capital of Jaipur State by Maharaja Sawai Jai Singh II.
